race.description: Ferndale Distributors Country Boosted Maiden Plate
race.comment: COLORADO SUN (6) finished second, beaten a head, when resuming from a spell last start over 1200m at this track. Is sure to have come on from that and is drawn much kinder over the longer trip. Shoulders plenty of upside and is clearly the one to beat. CAYMAN ISLAND (5) progressed nicely last time out to finish second when sent forward over this track and trip last time. Finds the maiden win elusive but doesn't need to improve much to break through this time. DIVINE SPARK (10) met with solid support last start here but could only manage seventh. It was almost too bad to be true, so expecting a sharp bounce back. INNA ZOU (12) has been good in her first two starts and will be further improved. Suspect she blends into the race nicely at the top of the straight and is poised to strike.
